ch\xc4\x81lit\xc4\x81 yena sa mukto n\xc4\x81tra sa\xe1\xb9\x83\xc5\x9baya\xe1\xb8\xa5 || 108 ||\n\nKu\xe1\xb9\x87\xe1\xb8\x8dali is of a bent shape, and has been described to be like a serpent. He\nwho has moved that \xc5\x9aakti is no doubt Mukta (released from bondage). 101.\n\np. 44\n\n\xe0\xa4\x97\xe0\xa4\x99\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\x97\xe0\xa4\xbe-\xe0\xa4\xaf\xe0\xa4\xae\xe0\xa5\x81\xe0\xa4\xa8\xe0\xa4\xaf\xe0\xa5\x8b\xe0\xa4\xb0\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xae\xe0\xa4\xa7\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xaf\xe0\xa5\x87 \xe0\xa4\xac\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xb2-\xe0\xa4\xb0\xe0\xa4\xa3\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xa1\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\x82 \xe0\xa4\xa4\xe0\xa4\xaa\xe0\xa4\xb8\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xb5\xe0\xa4\xbf\xe0\xa4\xa8\xe0\xa5\x80\xe0\xa4\xae |  \n\xe0\xa4\xac\xe0\xa4\xb2\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xa4\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\x95\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xb0\xe0\xa5\x87\xe0\xa4\xa3 \xe0\xa4\x97\xe0\xa5\x84\xe0\xa4\xb9\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xa3\xe0\xa5\x80\xe0\xa4\xaf\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xa4\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xa4\xe0\xa4\xa6\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xb5\xe0\xa4\xbf\xe0\xa4\xb7\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xb9\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xa3\xe0\xa5\x8b\xe0\xa4\x83 \xe0\xa4\xaa\xe0\xa4\xb0\xe0\xa4\xae\xe0\xa4\x82 \xe0\xa4\xaa\xe0\xa4\xa6\xe0\xa4\xae || \xe0\xa5\xa7\xe0\xa5\xa6\xe0\xa5\xaf ||\n\nghanggh\xc4\x81-yamunayormadhye b\xc4\x81la-ra\xe1\xb9\x87\xe1\xb8\x8d\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 tapasvin\xc4\xabm |  \nbal\xc4\x81tk\xc4\x81re\xe1\xb9\x87a gh\xe1\xb9\x9dh\xe1\xb9\x87\xc4\xaby\xc4\x81ttadvi\xe1\xb9\xa3h\xe1\xb9\x87o\xe1\xb8\xa5 parama\xe1\xb9\x83 padam || 109 ||\n\nYoungster Tapaswini (a she-ascetic), lying between the Ganges and the Yamuna,\n(Ida and Pingala) should be caught hold of by force, to get the highest\nposition. 102.\n\n\xe0\xa4\x87\xe0\xa4\xa1\xe0\xa4\xbe \xe0\xa4\xad\xe0\xa4\x97\xe0\xa4\xb5\xe0\xa4\xa4\xe0\xa5\x80 \xe0\xa4\x97\xe0\xa4\x99\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\x97\xe0\xa4\xb