e\xe1\xb9\xa3h\xe1\xb9\xadit\xc4\x81mbara-lak\xe1\xb9\xa3ha\xe1\xb9\x87am || 113 ||\n\nThe bulb is above the anus, a vitasti (12 angulas) long, and measures 4\nangulas (3 inches) in extent and is soft and white, and appears as if a folded\ncloth. 106.\n\n\xe0\xa4\xb8\xe0\xa4\xa4\xe0\xa4\xbf \xe0\xa4\xb5\xe0\xa4\x9c\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xb0\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xb8\xe0\xa4\xa8\xe0\xa5\x87 \xe0\xa4\xaa\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xa6\xe0\xa5\x8c \xe0\xa4\x95\xe0\xa4\xb0\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xad\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xaf\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\x82 \xe0\xa4\xa7\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xb0\xe0\xa4\xaf\xe0\xa5\x87\xe0\xa4\xa6\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xa6\xe0\xa5\x84\xe0\xa4\xa2\xe0\xa4\xae |  \n\xe0\xa4\x97\xe0\xa5\x81\xe0\xa4\xb2\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xab-\xe0\xa4\xa6\xe0\xa5\x87\xe0\xa4\xb6-\xe0\xa4\xb8\xe0\xa4\xae\xe0\xa5\x80\xe0\xa4\xaa\xe0\xa5\x87 \xe0\xa4\x9b \xe0\xa4\x95\xe0\xa4\xa8\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xa6\xe0\xa4\x82 \xe0\xa4\xa4\xe0\xa4\xa4\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xb0 \xe0\xa4\xaa\xe0\xa4\xb0\xe0\xa4\xaa\xe0\xa5\x80\xe0\xa4\xa1\xe0\xa4\xaf\xe0\xa5\x87\xe0\xa4\xa4 || \xe0\xa5\xa7\xe0\xa5\xa7\xe0\xa5\xaa ||\n\nsati vajr\xc4\x81sane p\xc4\x81dau kar\xc4\x81bhy\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 dh\xc4\x81rayedd\xe1\xb9\x9d\xe1\xb8\x8dham |  \nghulpha-de\xc5\x9ba-sam\xc4\xabpe cha kanda\xe1\xb9\x83 tatra prap\xc4\xab\xe1\xb8\x8dayet || 114 ||\n\nKeeping the feet in Vajra-asana (Padma-asana), hold them firmly with the\nhands. The position of the bulb then will be near the ankle joint, where it\nshould be pressed. 107.\n\n\xe0\xa4\xb5\xe0\xa4\x9c\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xb0\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xb8\xe0\xa4\xa8\xe0\xa5\x87 \xe0\xa4\xb8\xe0\xa4\xa5\xe0\xa4\xbf\xe0\xa4\xa4\xe0\xa5\x8b \xe0\xa4\xaf\xe0\xa5\x8b\xe0\xa4\x97\xe0\xa5\x80 \xe0\xa4\x9b\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xb2\xe0\xa4\xaf\xe0\xa4\xbf\xe0\xa4\xa4\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xb5\xe0\xa4\xbe \xe0\xa4\x9b \xe0\xa4\x95\xe0\xa5\x81\xe0\xa4\xa3\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xa1\xe0