81 \xc5\x9bakti\xe1\xb8\xa5 sa yogh\xc4\xab siddhi-bh\xc4\x81janam |  \nkimatra bahunoktena k\xc4\x81la\xe1\xb9\x83 jayati l\xc4\xablay\xc4\x81 || 120 ||\n\nThe Yogi, who has been able to move the \xc5\x9aakti deserves success. It is useless\nto say more, suffice it to say that he conquers death playfully. 113.\n\n\xe0\xa4\xac\xe0\xa4\xb0\xe0\xa4\xb9\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xae\xe0\xa4\x9b\xe0\xa4\xb0\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xaf-\xe0\xa4\xb0\xe0\xa4\xa4\xe0\xa4\xb8\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xaf\xe0\xa5\x88\xe0\xa4\xb5 \xe0\xa4\xa8\xe0\xa4\xbf\xe0\xa4\xa4\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xaf\xe0\xa4\x82 \xe0\xa4\xb9\xe0\xa4\xbf\xe0\xa4\xa4-\xe0\xa4\xae\xe0\xa4\xbf\xe0\xa4\xa4\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xb6\xe0\xa4\xbf\xe0\xa4\xa8\xe0\xa4\x83 |  \n\xe0\xa4\xae\xe0\xa4\xa3\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xa1\xe0\xa4\xb2\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xa6\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xa6\xe0\xa5\x84\xe0\xa4\xb6\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xaf\xe0\xa4\xa4\xe0\xa5\x87 \xe0\xa4\xb8\xe0\xa4\xbf\xe0\xa4\xa6\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xa7\xe0\xa4\xbf\xe0\xa4\x83 \xe0\xa4\x95\xe0\xa5\x81\xe0\xa4\xa3\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xa1\xe0\xa4\xb2\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xaf-\xe0\xa4\x85\xe0\xa4\xad\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xaf\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xb8-\xe0\xa4\xaf\xe0\xa5\x8b\xe0\xa4\x97\xe0\xa4\xbf\xe0\xa4\xa8\xe0\xa4\x83 || \xe0\xa5\xa7\xe0\xa5\xa8\xe0\xa5\xa7 ||\n\nbrahmacharya-ratasyaiva nitya\xe1\xb9\x83 hita-mit\xc4\x81\xc5\x9bina\xe1\xb8\xa5 |  \nma\xe1\xb9\x87\xe1\xb8\x8dal\xc4\x81dd\xe1\xb9\x9d\xc5\x9byate siddhi\xe1\xb8\xa5 ku\xe1\xb9\x87\xe1\xb8\x8daly-abhy\xc4\x81sa-yoghina\xe1\xb8\xa5 || 121 ||\n\nThe Yogi observing Brahmacharya (continence and always eating sparingly, gets\nsuccess within 40 days by practice with the Ku\xe1\xb9\x87\xe1\xb8\x8dalini. 114.\n\n\xe0\xa4\x95\xe0\xa5\x81\xe0\xa4\xa3\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xa1\xe0\xa4\xb2\xe0\xa5\x80\xe0\xa4\x82 \xe0\xa4\x9b\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xb2\xe0\xa4\xaf\xe0\xa4\xbf\xe0\xa4\xa