-yukta\xe1\xb9\x83 samabhyaset |  \nitaratra na kartavy\xc4\x81 mano-v\xe1\xb9\x9dttirman\xc4\xab\xe1\xb9\xa3hi\xe1\xb9\x87\xc4\x81 || 127 ||\n\nAll the practices relating to the air should be performed with concentrated\nmind. A wise man should not allow his mind to wander away. 120.\n\n\xe0\xa4\x87\xe0\xa4\xa4\xe0\xa4\xbf \xe0\xa4\xae\xe0\xa5\x81\xe0\xa4\xa6\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xb0\xe0\xa4\xbe \xe0\xa4\xa6\xe0\xa4\xb6 \xe0\xa4\xaa\xe0\xa4\xb0\xe0\xa5\x8b\xe0\xa4\x95\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xa4\xe0\xa4\xbe \xe0\xa4\x86\xe0\xa4\xa6\xe0\xa4\xbf\xe0\xa4\xa8\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xa5\xe0\xa5\x87\xe0\xa4\xa8 \xe0\xa4\xb6\xe0\xa4\xae\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xad\xe0\xa5\x81\xe0\xa4\xa8\xe0\xa4\xbe |  \n\xe0\xa4\x8f\xe0\xa4\x95\xe0\xa5\x88\xe0\xa4\x95\xe0\xa4\xbe \xe0\xa4\xa4\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xb8\xe0\xa5\x81 \xe0\xa4\xaf\xe0\xa4\xae\xe0\xa4\xbf\xe0\xa4\xa8\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\x82 \xe0\xa4\xae\xe0\xa4\xb9\xe0\xa4\xbe-\xe0\xa4\xb8\xe0\xa4\xbf\xe0\xa4\xa6\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xa7\xe0\xa4\xbf-\xe0\xa4\xaa\xe0\xa4\xb0\xe0\xa4\xa6\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xaf\xe0\xa4\xbf\xe0\xa4\xa8\xe0\xa5\x80 || \xe0\xa5\xa7\xe0\xa5\xa8\xe0\xa5\xae ||\n\niti mudr\xc4\x81 da\xc5\x9ba prokt\xc4\x81 \xc4\x81din\xc4\x81thena \xc5\x9bambhun\xc4\x81 |  \nekaik\xc4\x81 t\xc4\x81su yamin\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 mah\xc4\x81-siddhi-prad\xc4\x81yin\xc4\xab || 128 ||\n\nThese are the Mudras, as explained by \xc3\x82dinatha (\xc5\x9aiva). Every one of them is\nthe giver of great accomplishments to the practiser. 121.\n\n\xe0\xa4\x89\xe0\xa4\xaa\xe0\xa4\xa6\xe0\xa5\x87\xe0\xa4\xb6\xe0\xa4\x82 \xe0\xa4\xb9\xe0\xa4\xbf \xe0\xa4\xae\xe0\xa5\x81\xe0\xa4\xa6\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xb0\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xa3\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\x82 \xe0\xa4\xaf\xe0\xa5\x8b \xe0\xa4\xa6\xe0\xa4\xa4\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xa4\xe0\xa5\x87 \xe0\xa4\xb8\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xae\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xaa\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xb0\xe0\xa4\xa6\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xaf\xe0\xa4\xbf\xe0\xa4\x95\xe0\xa4\xae |  \n\xe0\xa4\xb8 \xe0\xa4\x8f\xe0\xa4\xb5 \xe0\xa4\xb6\xe0\xa4\xb0\xe0\xa5\x80-\xe0\xa4\x97\xe0\xa5\x81\xe0\xa4\xb0\xe0\xa5\x81\xe0\xa4\x83 \xe0\xa4\xb8\xe0\xa4\xb5\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xae\xe0\xa5\x80 \xe0\xa4\xb8\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\x95\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xb7\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xb9\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xa6\xe0\xa5\x80\xe0\xa4\xb6\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xb5\xe0\xa4\xb0 \xe0\xa4\x8f\xe0\xa4\xb5 \xe0\xa4\xb8\xe0\xa4\x83 || \xe0\xa5\xa7\xe0\xa5\xa8\xe0\xa5\xaf ||\n\nupade\xc5\x9ba\xe1\xb9\x83 hi mudr\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x87\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 yo datte s\xc4\x81mprad\xc4\x81yikam |  \nsa eva \xc5\x9br\xc4\xab-ghuru\xe1\xb8\xa5 sv\xc4\x81m\xc4\xab s\xc4\x81k\xe1\xb9\xa3h\xc4\x81d\xc4\xab\xc5\x9bvara eva sa\xe1\xb8\xa5 || 129 ||\n\nHe is really the _guru_ and to be considered as \xc3\x8e\xc5\x9bvara in human form who\nteaches the Mudras as handed down from guru to guru. 122.\n\n\xe0\xa4\xa4\xe0\xa4\xb8\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xaf \xe0\xa4\xb5\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\x95\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xaf-\xe0\xa4\xaa\xe0\xa4\xb0\xe0\xa5\x8b \xe0\xa4\xad\xe0\xa5\x82\xe0\xa4\xa4\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xb5\xe0\xa4\xbe \xe0\xa4\xae\xe0\xa5\x81\xe0\xa4\xa6\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xb0\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xad\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xaf\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xb8\xe0\xa5\x87 \xe0\xa4\xb8\xe0\xa4\xae\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xb9\xe0\xa4\xbf\xe0\xa4\xa4\xe0\xa4\x83 |  \n\xe0\xa4\x85\xe0\xa4\xa3\xe0\xa4\xbf\xe0\xa4\xae\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xa6\xe0\xa4\xbf-\xe0\xa4\x97\xe0\xa5\x81\xe0\xa4\xa3\xe0\xa5\x88\xe0\xa4\x83 \xe0\xa4\xb8\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xb0\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\xa7\xe0\xa4\x82 \xe0\xa4\xb2\xe0\xa4\xad\xe0\xa4\xa4\xe0\xa5\x87 \xe0\xa4\x95\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xb2-\xe0\xa4\xb5\xe0\xa4\x9e\xc3\xa0\xc2\xa5\xc2\x8d\xe0\xa4\x9b\xe0\xa4\xa8\xe0\xa4\xae || \xe0\xa5\xa7\xe0\xa5\xa9\xe0\xa5\xa6 ||\n\ntasya v\xc4\x81kya-paro bh\xc5\xabtv\xc4\x81 mudr\xc4\x81bhy\xc4\x81se sam\xc4\x81hita\xe1\xb8\xa5 |  \na\xe1\xb9\x87im\xc4\x81di-ghu\xe1\xb9\x87ai\xe1\xb8\xa5 s\xc4\x81rdha\xe1\xb9\x83 labhate k\xc4\x81la-va\xc3\xb1chanam || 130 ||\n\nEngaging in practice, by putting faith in his words, one gets the Siddhis of\nAnima, etc., as also evades death. 123.\n\n_End of chapter III, on the Exposition of the Mudr as_.\n\n\xe0\xa4\x87\xe0\xa4\xa4\xe0\xa4\xbf \xe0\xa4\xb9\xe0\xa4\xa0-\xe0\xa4\xaa\xe0\xa4\xb0\xe0\xa4\xa6\xe0\xa5\x80\xe0\xa4\xaa\xe0\xa4\xbf\xe0\xa4\x95\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\xaf\xe0\xa4\xbe\xe0\xa4\x82 \xe0\xa4\xa4\xe0\xa5\x84\xe0\xa4\xa4\xe0\xa5\x80\xe0\xa4\xaf\xe0\xa5\x8b\xe0\xa4\xaa\xe0\xa4\xa6\xe0\xa5\x87\xe0\xa4\xb6\xe0\xa4\x83 |\n\niti ha\xe1\xb9\xadha-prad\xc4\xabpik\xc4\x81y\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 t\xe1\xb9\x9dt\xc4\xabyopade\xc5\x9ba\xe1\xb8\xa5 |\n\n* * *\n\n[Next: Chapter IV. On Samadhi.](hyp06.htm)\n\n"